precis:
Amendments (SCHEDULE No. 975) to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS which set
Maximum Residue Limits on the amount of the insecticide "ACEPHATE" that may
be detected on cranberries and on a variety of vegetables, and in the case
of its metabolite "METHAMIDOPHOS", the amount detected on beans.
